descriptions.en: On the day of her marriage, Lu Zhen makes an escape. She decides to go into the palace as a maid, but she needs a certificate of identification.
An Incident occurs due to Madam Zhao, but everything is blamed on Lu Zhen.

The Emperor Dies, and the throne is empty for he didn't announce his heir to the throne. Empress Lu takes the chance to get her son, Yan'er on the throne. The Late Emperor first wife's son, is announced dead, which brings smiles to Empress Lu.
